title: BONUS Ep. #10 | 'The Other Side' by Eric Nam
description:
The day has come! Eric Nam's 4th mini album "The Other Side" is available NOW! Tune in for a special announcement from Eric, and don't forget to stream all five tracks on Spotify, iTunes, Google Play, or wherever you get your music.


Make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow (IT’S FREE) and leave a comment, rating and/or review on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, Soundcloud, and YouTube.
